{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/local7/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"ed7c8c08-ccb4-540c-b21b-e89d17d949dd","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/local7/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived website without DB</a>\n</p>\n<p>Local7 contacted us (Webmarket) to build an online shop to sell their products. They wanted a very personal style combined with great UX and an easy payment method.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/f74889145875ba4821fde11b64d3079b/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f74889145875ba4821fde11b64d3079b/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/f74889145875ba4821fde11b64d3079b/dbdff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>At this point, I didn’t have a system or CMS with this sort of functionality. The open source options available at that time were also very insufficient for the requirements, so I decided to build my own bespoke solution. I called it TIENDAFlash, because it was based in Flash, PHP and MySQL.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/6450db87c4e76d73648a63633b1e2d8c/dbdff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6450db87c4e76d73648a63633b1e2d8c/d1f95/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/6450db87c4e76d73648a63633b1e2d8c/dbdff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>TIENDAFlash allows the maximum flexibility in the front-end and a very compatible and extended tech stack for the backend. It also features a custom CMS to add/edit/remove products, categories, photos and customers. I also implemented a credit/debit card payment gateway using the API from ServiRed (a very popular banking network in Spain).</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1066px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/9a5404d9a4a5ebf30b291dc75c093bbe/96cf6/5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9a5404d9a4a5ebf30b291dc75c093bbe/d1f95/5.jpg 500w,\n/static/9a5404d9a4a5ebf30b291dc75c093bbe/dbdff/5.jpg 1000w,\n/static/9a5404d9a4a5ebf30b291dc75c093bbe/96cf6/5.jpg 1066w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1066px) 100vw, 1066px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      clas